        <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">5</NUMEX>-y periods was <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">0.10</NUMEX> (<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">0.47</NUMEX>) h. For <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">190</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participants</ENAMEX> with <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">at least three</NUMEX> sleep diaries, the
