        <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Table 4</ENAMEX>; Figure <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">3A</NUMEX>). Measures of usual and one-night polysomnographically defined sleep
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">time</ENAMEX> were only weakly, but statistically significantly, correlated (
