        Hormone measurements were all performed on a single fasted, <TIMEX TYPE="TIME">morning</TIMEX> sample and may not
        reflect the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">24</NUMEX>-h profile. It is possible that <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participants</ENAMEX> with shorter sleep woke up
